name: R A J O G U N A
description:
[SIMULATANEON SERIES #012]

R A J O G U N A

A fickle candle procures short-range clarity during the Journey. It effortlessly dissipates whatever duality it comes in contact with. Just for a little while.

SIMULATANEON is a 2017 hypersigil and a conceptual prison break map for the upcoming matrix system update. The sigils that were borrowed for this series reveal only part of a bigger tapestry.
